Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.77,0:00:29.87,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,And this low pressure system\Nover the Sea of Japan...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.91,0:00:32.47,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,...will be bringing the\Nfirst spring breeze tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.51,0:00:35.07,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,Announcing both the\Nend of the long winter...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.12,0:00:36.67,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,...and the coming of spring.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.26,0:00:49.56,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,You really think a new girl\Ncan fill in for you, Michiko?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.60,0:00:52.86,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,It's just for one day.\NAnd it's only the weather corner.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.90,0:00:55.60,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you saying? In this day\Nand age, a weather report girl...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.64,0:00:59.47,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,...can be the secret idol of\Nsalary men and college students.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.51,0:01:01.27,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,Me? An idol?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.41,0:01:07.35,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,"KEIKO NAKADAI"
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.27,0:01:29.39,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, yes... Oh, yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.15,0:01:41.74,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh, Keiko? Are you in here?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.28,0:01:46.65,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,Who's there?!\NOf all the rotten timing...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.69,0:01:51.28,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry! But they want to\Nsee you in the news department.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.32,0:01:54.23,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,What do they want\Nme up there for?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.26,0:01:57.23,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh, well... I heard they\Nchose you to stand in for...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.26,0:02:00.63,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,...Michiko Kawai to do\Nthe weather corner.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.27,0:02:03.33,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,- Really?!\N- Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.28,0:02:13.34,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, why didn't you say so?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.33,0:02:29.30,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,Keiko!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.77,0:02:34.67,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,The day I've been waiting\Nfor has finally arrived!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.70,0:02:36.19,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,Wha...?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.18,0:02:50.17,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,WEATHER REPORT GIRL
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.72,0:02:59.62,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,These are the ratings for our\Ncompetition. And here are ATV's.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.26,0:03:09.19,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,ATV is coming in dead last\Nin the ratings race.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.34,0:03:13.29,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,It's terrible!\NEven out on the Ginza...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.34,0:03:17.40,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,...none of the girls can name\Na single one of our shows!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.24,0:03:23.38,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,Some of our sponsors have\Nalready said that if these...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.42,0:03:27.38,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,...ratings continue, they're\Ngoing to dump our programs!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.42,0:03:30.32,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,- Or so they say.\N- Then we have no choice!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.36,0:03:35.06,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,I say we get all the girls who\Nwork here to do a striptease!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.10,0:03:37.36,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe at the tail\Nend of prime time.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.40,0:03:39.73,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,I agree with him!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.77,0:03:41.39,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. Chairman!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.43,0:03:44.87,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,We musn't overlook any\Nmethod to survive this crisis!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.78,0:03:55.94,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,Sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.78,0:04:01.58,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,Whatever it takes, get those ratings...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.12,0:04:07.79,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,GET THOSE RATINGS UP!!!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.76,0:04:11.75,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,- Mr. Chairman!\N- Hang on, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.80,0:04:14.06,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. Chairman!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.41,0:04:24.43,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm really surprised.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.48,0:04:27.45,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,This picture looks nothing like you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.48,0:04:29.11,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, you think so?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.15,0:04:32.41,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,I've dressed like that since\NI started here a year ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.72,0:04:35.48,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,But why? You're so beautiful.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.52,0:04:37.49,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,Because this is a TV station...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.52,0:04:41.15,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,...and pretty girls like\Nme are a dime a dozen.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.19,0:04:44.13,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,Trying to be the flashiest\None won't get you anywhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.46,0:04:47.46,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,The clever eagle who\Nhides her claws, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.50,0:04:51.49,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, please! I don't\Nhave any claws to hide.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.74,0:04:54.83,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,Fangs, perhaps?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.41,0:05:02.51,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,I just want to get ahead.\NAnd I'll do whatever it takes.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.45,0:05:06.42,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,God, Kimura looks so stiff!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.45,0:05:08.92,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,Her wedding dress is beautiful, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.49,0:05:11.08,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, there's Michiko!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.12,0:05:14.42,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course she'd look beautiful on camera.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.46,0:05:17.12,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, she is ATV's star TV announcer.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.16,0:05:20.53,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,She made it the biggest of\Nanyone from our college class.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.80,0:05:28.40,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,Misuzu Tamaru started out as\Na weather girl. You know that?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.44,0:05:30.17,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,- Really? - Uh-huh.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.21,0:05:33.87,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,And Etsuko Koyama\Nstarted on a tabloid show.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.91,0:05:36.18,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,With your brains and your education...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.22,0:05:39.31,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,...I just know you'll go even\Nfurther than those two have!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.55,0:05:41.88,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I doubt that...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.92,0:05:44.86,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,Being able to interview you,\Nthe light of my college life...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.89,0:05:47.55,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,...would make becoming\Na reporter seem worth it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.50,0:05:51.55,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks, Samejima.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.90,0:05:58.86,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,The earthquake which shook the\NKanto area today caused...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.91,0:06:02.86,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,...an escalator to stop suddenly,\Ninjuring a group of...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.91,0:06:05.90,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,...high school students out on a class trip.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.25,0:06:09.91,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,The accident occurred on the Saikyo\Nplatform of the JR Shinjuku station.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.88,0:06:12.91,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,Miss Nakadai, it's almost time.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.19,0:06:14.59,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.61,0:06:39.57,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,Keiko Nakadai... I don't\Nknow how ugly you are...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.61,0:06:42.17,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,...but you're bound to make\Nme look great in comparison.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.22,0:06:44.95,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why I chose you!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.52,0:06:49.51,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,And now the weather.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.56,0:06:53.18,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,Filling in for Michiko Kawai\Nis a new announcer here at ATV.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.23,0:06:56.96,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,Miss Keiko Nakadai. Go ahead, Keiko.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.83,0:07:02.46,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,WEATHER CORNER
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.97,0:07:06.60,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,Good evening. This is Keiko Nakadai.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.91,0:07:10.07,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,The first spring winds blew\Nthrough the Kanto region today.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.91,0:07:14.31,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,Who... Who is she?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.35,0:07:17.98,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,The abnormal weather brought a\Ndownpour to the northeast...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.02,0:07:22.45,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,...causing damage in some parts.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.26,0:07:25.32,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,Turning now to Hokkaido--
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.36,0:07:27.33,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,- Who is she? - She's great!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.06,0:07:30.00,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,Keiko...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.03,0:07:33.29,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,Hokkaido was hit with an\Nunseasonably heavy snow storm...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.33,0:07:36.00,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,...with Asahikawa getting 40 cm.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.64,0:07:41.01,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,This skirt I'm wearing is 10 cm\Nabove my knees, so 40 would be...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.54,0:07:44.01,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,...about this deep!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.03,0:08:11.06,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,You idiot! Look what you've done!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.37,0:08:13.00,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,This isn't some midnight sex show!.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.04,0:08:15.67,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a decent 9:00 news program!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.71,0:08:17.57,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,If you want to show\Nyour panties to anyone...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.61,0:08:20.37,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,...then show 'em to your boyfriend!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.41,0:08:24.25,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,My boyfriend would get to see\Nwhat's BEHIND my panties!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.06,0:08:30.61,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,That little tramp!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.66,0:08:34.68,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,And you should complain only\Nwhen nobody watches the show!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.73,0:08:37.22,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,"A decent 9:00 news program?"
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.76,0:08:41.63,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,All the viewers care about is\Nwhat tie the anchorman's wearing...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.67,0:08:44.03,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,...and what the co-anchor's legs\Nlook like under her miniskirt!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.07,0:08:46.40,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,What did you...? You...!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.81,0:08:56.75,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, he's in. Mr. Higemasa, telephone.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.78,0:09:00.08,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm busy! Tell 'em to call back!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.12,0:09:02.68,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,But, it's the chief!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.72,0:09:04.38,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.42,0:09:06.05,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,Gimme that!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.09,0:09:11.39,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, sir. Sorry, sir.\NIt'll never happen again.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.73,0:09:19.54,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, sir. Of course.\NI'll... Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.74,0:09:26.08,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,The chairman caught\Nlast night's news cast.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.11,0:09:29.41,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,Last night's? But he was in the hospital.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.45,0:09:33.75,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,...is 10 cm above my knees,\Nso 40 would be...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.79,0:09:35.78,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,...about this deep!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.82,0:09:42.46,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,The Weather Corner really made him\Nfeel good in his hospital bed.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.80,0:09:48.76,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,From now on, News PM 9's\Nweather report girl...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.80,0:09:53.47,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,Keiko Nakadai! It will be you!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.11,0:09:59.10,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,Trouble! Everyone's calling in\Nabout Miss Nakadai last night!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.15,0:10:01.11,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,The phones are jammed!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.15,0:10:04.14,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,Our ratings last night jumped 15%!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.18,0:10:06.48,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,They haven't been that\Ngood since the Gulf War!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.49,0:10:11.96,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.13,0:10:16.80,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,No problem!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.83,0:10:21.49,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,If I'm wet, it's only because of the rain.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.80,0:10:24.20,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,But if I can't sleep,\Nthat's because of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.20,0:10:26.57,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,What a beautiful day!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.51,0:10:30.17,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,But if I can't sleep, that's because of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.51,0:10:36.51,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,Everywhere I go, people\Njust seem to irritate me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.85,0:10:45.15,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,So all I do is just take a\Ndeep breath and try to go on.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.19,0:10:51.86,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,A woman's heart is like the\Nchanging weather, you see.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.80,0:10:59.17,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,And a kiss like that isn't\Nenough to set it ablaze.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.21,0:11:02.54,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,After the rain stops, let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.48,0:11:06.38,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's get our hearts racing along.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.18,0:11:13.88,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,When it clears up,\Nwe'll love like it's paradise.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.19,0:11:18.45,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,After the rain stops, let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.49,0:11:22.15,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's both just lose control.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.19,0:11:25.22,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll hold you like...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.24,0:11:34.54,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, it's 9:30. Pops! Change the channel
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.57,0:11:35.37,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,Gotcha.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.91,0:11:39.57,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,Hi there! It's weather time again.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.25,0:11:44.84,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm coming to you tonight from\Nunder the blooming cherry trees.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.59,0:11:48.25,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,This alone gives joy\Nto my dreary existence.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.29,0:11:49.85,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,Can't argue with you there.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.89,0:11:52.82,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,So, did you students taking\Nyour entrance exams do well
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.86,0:11:54.88,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,Or not so well?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.93,0:11:58.89,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,Not so well. I screwed up my fourth try.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.93,0:12:02.89,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,Spring is still young.\NEnjoy it while you can.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.94,0:12:05.60,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,And for those who didn't\Nmake it, hang in there.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.57,0:12:08.27,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,Throw out your chests.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.94,0:12:10.60,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,Like THlS!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.28,0:12:16.04,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,Keiko...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.55,0:12:23.95,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to be with you!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.93,0:12:30.62,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,You should be more careful, Keiko.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.66,0:12:31.86,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.90,0:12:35.66,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't know who's watching\Nyou on TV, or where they are.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.70,0:12:39.60,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,If you turn on the wrong kind of\Nguy, you could end up in trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.64,0:12:40.97,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,Did I turn you guys on?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.01,0:12:44.57,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,- You were really sexy!\N- The absolute best!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.61,0:12:45.77,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,They seemed to like it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.81,0:12:50.04,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,If you do get in trouble,\Nno one'll be there to help you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.62,0:12:56.32,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,I know that. Perfectly.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.26,0:13:05.79,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,It must have fallen in during my report.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.30,0:13:08.63,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,Mine! Mine!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.67,0:13:11.33,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,All right! Here's some more for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.36,0:13:34.72,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,I've come about the part-time job.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.30,0:13:43.67,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,So here I am.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.70,0:13:46.93,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm supposed to be applying\Nto that prep school.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.97,0:13:49.03,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,What am I doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.99,0:14:02.28,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,Keiko!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.32,0:14:04.69,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,What's the hold up?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.72,0:14:07.99,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,- I just wanted to see you...\N- Autograph? Some other time.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.03,0:14:10.69,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on! Crack it open!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.73,0:14:12.06,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, right...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.40,0:14:18.50,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,There we go!\NI'm so hungry I could scream!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.71,0:14:22.70,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,Keiko.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.74,0:14:24.94,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you remember me?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.75,0:14:27.34,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,"Me?"
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.38,0:14:30.41,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,Yamagishi, from high school.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.45,0:14:35.05,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,Yama-what?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.09,0:14:36.75,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,Yamagishi.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.02,0:14:40.75,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, yeah! Hey, it's been a while!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.03,0:14:46.76,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,You were with us on\Ngraduation night, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.70,0:14:52.10,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.79,0:15:09.45,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,Yamagishi...Weird guy...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.82,0:15:13.12,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,Yamagishi!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.43,0:15:18.80,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,So, Mr. Class 3 Yamagishi!\NYou want to lay me, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.47,0:15:25.16,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,- No shit? - Let him do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.47,0:15:29.46,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,Keiko, in front of everyone?!\NHow could you?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.38,0:15:35.47,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,What's that mean? What do you\Nthink we'd do if we were alone?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.53,0:15:51.09,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,You wanna see me naked?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.83,0:15:56.43,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,I feel so hot. Why don't I undress?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.54,0:16:37.53,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,Keiko Nakadai's Greatest Mistake!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.58,0:16:39.67,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,I can never hold my alcohol.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.28,0:16:43.21,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,I wasted myself on that\Nlittle piece of filth!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.55,0:16:51.32,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,So what? All he did was see me naked.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.49,0:16:57.76,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,No, wait! It didn't end there.\NSomething else happened...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.57,0:17:03.23,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,Take your clothes off, too!\NDon't let Keiko be the only one!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.27,0:17:05.24,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,Cut it out, you...!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.91,0:17:08.24,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,Look! Keiko's sick!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.91,0:17:10.90,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna puke...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.58,0:17:13.07,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,Get a bowl!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.11,0:17:16.51,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,No, it's coming! Plug my mouth!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.55,0:17:18.52,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,"Plug it?"
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.31,0:17:45.61,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.25,0:17:54.28,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,You there. Wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.96,0:17:58.62,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,Take this to Miss Nakadai,\Nthe weathercaster.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.99,0:18:02.29,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, just for her.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.96,0:18:08.26,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,Careful. She can be a real\Nterror when she's hungry.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.30,0:18:10.27,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.30,0:18:13.27,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,About Keiko. I'm...an old friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.54,0:18:17.24,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, you don't say?\NWell, see that she gets it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.64,0:18:19.30,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.15,0:18:24.88,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,Aren't you Michiko Kawai,\Nthe old weather girl?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.62,0:18:28.95,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,They moved me over to morning news.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.99,0:18:32.65,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,It's because I can't be as flashy as she is.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.29,0:18:35.99,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,Compared to her, I'm nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.03,0:18:38.79,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,That's not true! That's not true at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.27,0:18:46.00,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks. Nice meeting you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.05,0:19:00.68,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me, Keiko. I gave you the wrong...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.32,0:19:07.59,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, you already ate it?\NWhat do I do with this?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.37,0:19:19.36,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,YOU EAT IT!!!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.05,0:19:35.01,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing here?!\NI'd almost forgotten about it!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.05,0:19:37.22,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,Now I remember it all!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.39,0:19:42.22,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,Just disappear! Or drop dead!\NYou little insect!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.66,0:19:48.72,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,You can't really mean that!\NI still love you...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.07,0:19:51.66,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,Just go away!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.70,0:19:54.47,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,I'd forget the whole thing in\Nfour seconds if you just left!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.74,0:19:58.40,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll stomp that ugly little dick of yours flat!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.74,0:20:00.37,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you understand?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.41,0:20:03.40,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,Your teeth marks are still all over it!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.09,0:20:11.05,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,No woman can love me when\Nanother woman's teeth marks...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.09,0:20:14.06,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,...are all over my dick!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.09,0:20:16.69,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,You've scarred me for life!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.73,0:20:19.16,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,You're the only woman\NI can ever have now!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.40,0:20:21.33,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up! Just shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.37,0:20:24.73,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll never drink again!\NOr even show my panties!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.77,0:20:27.10,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be a good girl!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.11,0:20:31.44,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,I always just wanted\Nto be a nice girl!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.38,0:20:35.11,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,Keiko...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.78,0:20:38.44,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,What the...?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.42,0:20:42.35,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,Why's my stomach...?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.49,0:20:49.46,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,Keiko, what's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.16,0:20:54.46,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, well...\NMy dear predecessor, Miss Kawai.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.50,0:20:57.77,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,What brings you to my dressing room?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.80,0:21:00.74,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,Must get to toilet...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.77,0:21:05.30,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,No! Can't move! If I do...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.88,0:21:09.14,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,You're always attacking people!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.18,0:21:12.12,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,That's not the way you\Nshould act when you work!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.15,0:21:14.14,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,No, I don't want to argue with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.19,0:21:18.12,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if I was logical about it,\Nthey'd just call it a girls fight.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.16,0:21:20.13,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,Especially considering your short temper.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.16,0:21:21.79,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,You're pretty cool\Nand you know the score.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.83,0:21:24.49,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,But I'M the popular one.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.10,0:21:30.13,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,I have to be here every day at 4:00 am!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.17,0:21:33.10,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,It's your fault I'm stuck\Ndoing "Weather at Dawn!"
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.14,0:21:35.77,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,While you get to party in Roppongi...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.81,0:21:38.57,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,...I have to go to sleep\Nearly like some little kid!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.18,0:21:43.81,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,If you hate it, then flash a\Nlittle panty and get popular.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.15,0:21:47.85,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, for heaven's sake!\NYou sound like a kid!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.86,0:21:52.85,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,Give it a try! Lift that ol' skirt high!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.53,0:22:04.53,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,Just thinking all the time\Ndoesn't get anything done.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.90,0:22:33.89,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,That idiot must've eaten some.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.87,0:22:38.17,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe it's for the best.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.20,0:22:41.20,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,Who knows what sort of terrible\Nvengeance she'd exact...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.24,0:22:44.97,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,...if she found out\NI poisoned her food.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.31,0:22:48.91,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,I need a safer, more secure way.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.29,0:22:59.85,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,Keiko. You seem to\Nhave a lot of enemies.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.89,0:23:00.92,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,Enemies?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.96,0:23:05.19,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,A dog got into your room\Nafter the accident.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.23,0:23:06.53,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,A dog?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.57,0:23:08.56,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,They were using it in\None of the other shows.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.60,0:23:13.56,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,It ran into your room\Nand ate some of that lunch.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.61,0:23:16.23,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,- And? - Same thing happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.28,0:23:19.57,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,Just like the part-timer.\NTurned his guts to water.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.61,0:23:22.91,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,- You mean...? - The lunch was doped.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.95,0:23:28.58,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,That pork cutlet was covered\Nwith dissolved laxative.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.62,0:23:29.55,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,Laxative?!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.30,0:23:40.93,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, spill it! Who gave you the lunch?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.97,0:23:48.91,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,I have proof! It was covered with laxative!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.94,0:23:52.07,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,Only someone working\Nhere could have done it!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.61,0:23:58.64,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,You're the real victim here.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.32,0:24:03.55,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,You disgraced yourself in public.\NLost your human dignity.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.99,0:24:08.65,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,Someone's responsible.\NWhy take the fall for them?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.70,0:24:15.63,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,If... If I say who did it,\Nwhat will you do?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.00,0:24:19.94,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,Just ask them not to do it again.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.97,0:24:21.96,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,Bullshit! I bet you'd kill them!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.01,0:24:27.50,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, so you're covering for them!\NYou're in on this conspiracy?!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:29.01,0:24:33.68,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,You protected me this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:34.02,0:24:35.95,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorta grateful to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:38.66,0:24:43.69,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,I was thinking I could keep\Nyou around as a bodyguard.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:49.70,0:24:53.66,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,It was... Michiko Kawai.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:58.01,0:25:01.00,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,What? Keiko can't go on tonight?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:01.05,0:25:04.02,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,Said she overdid the karaoke last night.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:04.05,0:25:07.04,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,Cracked my voice on a Chages medley.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:08.05,0:25:10.61,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, that's the story.\NCan you fill in tonight?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:11.39,0:25:12.95,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:21.33,0:25:24.73,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,I can do this! If brains and\Neducation won't let me win...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:24.77,0:25:27.74,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,...I can still do it on looks alone!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:31.78,0:25:35.08,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't lose to a woman like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:39.68,0:25:42.02,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,This is my chance to\Nget back into prime time!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:42.05,0:25:47.18,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,The ratings are at 20%\NCan't be too hard to keep 'em.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:50.76,0:25:52.99,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,Tea for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:53.03,0:25:55.02,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks. Leave it there.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:55.07,0:25:57.09,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, miss. Excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:16.09,0:26:18.45,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,She actually drank it!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:19.46,0:26:21.12,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,Too bad for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:26.10,0:26:28.19,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,NEWS PM 9
Dialogue: 0,0:26:31.47,0:26:33.70,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,Good evening, this is News PM 9.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:33.74,0:26:35.73,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm anchorman Hijikata.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:35.77,0:26:37.80,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,And I'm co-anchor Kondo.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:52.12,0:26:56.75,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,Calm down. It's in the bag. Don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:00.20,0:27:03.00,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,Almost time, Miss Kawai. Get ready.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:03.84,0:27:04.82,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:19.22,0:27:22.48,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,Good evening. Michiko Kawai here.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:22.52,0:27:27.22,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be filling in for\NMiss Nakadai this evening.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:27.86,0:27:29.16,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,Here we go.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:29.19,0:27:33.76,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,Jeez... She's going all out\Nfor just one night's work.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:33.80,0:27:36.16,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,Doubt the ratings'll drop tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:36.20,0:27:38.47,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,God, I love working here!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:38.84,0:27:43.17,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,That low pressure system which\Nbrought heavy rains to Kyushu...
Dialogue: 0,0:27:43.21,0:27:44.84,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,What's the point?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:44.88,0:27:48.97,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,She's six years older than me\Nand still trying to compete!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:49.28,0:27:52.91,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,We should see heavy rains\Nhit the Pacific Coast as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:53.85,0:27:58.19,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,Like this? Is this the way you like it?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:58.22,0:28:00.85,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,God, you viewers are all idiots.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:00.89,0:28:04.38,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,You couldn't understand\Nanything complicated.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:10.57,0:28:13.20,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,Okinawa's already seeing its rainy season.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:13.24,0:28:15.23,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,This week, Kyushu will also be...
Dialogue: 0,0:28:19.18,0:28:20.58,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell?!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:30.26,0:28:31.95,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,And... And, uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:28:34.13,0:28:34.96,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,"What's wrong? Go on."
Dialogue: 0,0:28:35.59,0:28:38.89,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,In Kyushu this week...
Dialogue: 0,0:28:48.91,0:28:51.21,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,There it goes.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:51.24,0:28:56.87,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,I spiked that tea you drank\Nwith gorilla-laxative.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:57.62,0:29:00.28,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,Your stomach'll be going\Nthrough hell in a minute.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:01.29,0:29:05.92,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,Laxative? Keiko Nakadai!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:05.96,0:29:08.29,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,But when? How?!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:11.93,0:29:13.63,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,Excellent brandy...
Dialogue: 0,0:29:16.64,0:29:21.13,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,By next week, the entire country\Nwill be in the rainy season.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:22.27,0:29:26.11,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,What'll I do?! Say "Excuse me,\NI have to take a crap really bad?"
Dialogue: 0,0:29:27.31,0:29:34.31,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,No way in hell. If I did that,\Nthey'd can me for sure!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:35.39,0:29:37.01,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,"Three minutes. Hurry!"
Dialogue: 0,0:29:37.72,0:29:39.75,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,Three minutes left!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:40.33,0:29:44.28,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,These two masses of sea air\Nwill...move in over...
Dialogue: 0,0:29:44.33,0:29:47.92,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,...the islands...and bring\Nthe rainy season to us!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:47.97,0:29:49.33,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,You won't beat me, Keiko Nakadai!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:49.37,0:29:55.14,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll show you just how tight\Nthose gymnastics made my ass!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:56.98,0:29:58.31,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:58.34,0:30:01.94,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,These two masses of sea air\Npushing together are...
Dialogue: 0,0:30:01.98,0:30:05.94,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,Something's wrong with Michiko.\NShould we cut away?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:05.98,0:30:07.71,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,We've got two minutes.\NLet her go on.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:08.95,0:30:13.01,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,If one of the masses is\Nstronger, the pressure will...
Dialogue: 0,0:30:15.33,0:30:17.69,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, yes! You've got it bad!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:29.37,0:30:32.97,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm just doing to you what\Nyou were going to do to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:35.01,0:30:37.07,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,An eye for an eye.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:40.72,0:30:46.42,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,As these masses push against...\NPush against...each other...
Dialogue: 0,0:31:21.76,0:31:25.09,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,No use... Can't hold it! I can't...
Dialogue: 0,0:31:30.37,0:31:32.46,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,Chance of rain tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:37.08,0:31:39.07,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,Chance of rain...
Dialogue: 0,0:31:45.45,0:31:48.78,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,Chance...of...rain...!!!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:24.09,0:32:27.46,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,The boss said he wanted to fire you.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:27.49,0:32:33.12,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,They can't do that! I'd have to\Nstart my career all over again!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:33.16,0:32:36.50,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,If you agree to be my assistant,\NI could change his mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:36.53,0:32:39.50,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't! I'd sooner be fired!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:40.47,0:32:44.50,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, they gave me a private\Noffice, but forgot the chair.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:46.88,0:32:50.34,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. Don't worry.\NMy assistant's helping out.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:51.48,0:32:54.51,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,What's that? Don't worry.\NTalk to you later.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:56.82,0:33:00.69,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,I have an apartment nearby.\NThose are the keys.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:18.88,0:33:20.87,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,I want these panties washed!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:24.58,0:33:28.11,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,You're going to use the machine\Nthis late at night?!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:28.15,0:33:31.21,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,Use your tongue! Lick 'em clean!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:38.86,0:33:42.23,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,That's the way. You'll do that every day.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:00.52,0:34:03.89,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,I've been getting the oddest\Nfeeling in my back.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:03.92,0:34:07.59,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,You make a lot of strange\Nacquaintances as a reporter.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:26.61,0:34:28.94,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,We got some real winners here.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:30.62,0:34:33.45,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,We've been waitin' for ya!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:33.55,0:34:37.61,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,Great. We get paid to do a gal like this!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:38.66,0:34:41.85,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, Keiko... You will die!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:42.23,0:34:46.96,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,You can't get away.\NJust relax and lose the clothes.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:47.67,0:34:50.93,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,All right then. I'm game for a fight.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:56.94,0:34:58.10,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,That's better.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:11.26,0:35:12.31,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,Why, you...!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:17.16,0:35:19.15,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll break it!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:52.30,0:35:57.03,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,It's your fault! Shoulda just\Nlet us do you in the first place!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:25.30,0:36:27.39,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,Michiko, save yourself!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:34.37,0:36:39.74,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,Someday...I'll write a book about you...!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:04.74,0:37:07.50,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,The panties I cleaned...
Dialogue: 0,0:37:10.74,0:37:13.40,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,How could I have\Nknown you knew karate?!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:13.44,0:37:16.78,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,I've washed you so many times,\Nbut l've never seen any bruises.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:17.32,0:37:20.34,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,Not even a single scratch!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:23.25,0:37:26.78,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,Fool! I am a genius at everything!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:40.64,0:37:43.16,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,"Tetsudo-ltoh Karate\NCorrespondence Course Now Ended."
Dialogue: 0,0:37:56.75,0:38:00.16,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,Is it love or just infatuation?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:00.19,0:38:03.79,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't need that kind of talk from you.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:03.83,0:38:06.80,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, but this whole thing\Njust isn't fun anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:06.83,0:38:10.82,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,See you again.\NYeah, in a hundred years!
Dialogue: 0,0:38:10.87,0:38:14.40,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,The burning I feel in my heart...
Dialogue: 0,0:38:14.44,0:38:17.84,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,...burns for lot more guys than you.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:17.88,0:38:21.20,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,When you burn for her,\Nbut she's not there for you...
Dialogue: 0,0:38:21.21,0:38:24.80,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,...is when a girl seems\Nto shine brighter still!
Dialogue: 0,0:38:24.85,0:38:31.85,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,I take my time as I strip off my clothes.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:31.89,0:38:39.19,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,Shining bright in just my naked skin.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:39.93,0:38:47.20,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,On a passion-filled vacation,\NI don't want this to ever end.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:47.87,0:38:54.18,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, this dazzling sky,\NI wanna hold it close to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:38:54.21,0:39:01.21,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,On a passion-filled vacation,\Nin a fire we build on our own.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:02.15,0:39:08.56,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,Burning on and on, wherever we go.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:35.22,0:39:42.09,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,On a passion-filled vacation,\NI wanna reach up and embrace the sun.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:43.26,0:39:49.26,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,Wanna be free and let my passions ignite.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:49.30,0:39:56.43,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,On a passion-filled vacation,\NI'll let my troubles sleep it away.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:57.21,0:40:04.27,WRG,,0000,0000,0000,,As I stand alone in the flowing breeze.
